    "caption": "⚡️ Battle of the Bay 2026 ⚡️\n\nWe’re switching up 🛸 Battle of the Bay 🛸 a bit this year with a special format: sport climbing!\n\nThis year marks a decade 🙀 since our last Open Category sport climbing finals event (who remembers TRS 2016?!). We couldn’t be more thrilled to bring the energy ⚡️ back to where we left off: Mission Cliffs.\n\nEvent Schedule\n 🗓️March 27: Open Category Qualifiers\n 🗓️March 28: Citizens Round, Happy Hour, Open Category Finals\n\nCategories: \n 🕺Men’s\n 💃Women’s\n 🤸Non-Binary\n\nCash Purse: \n 🤑 $9,000+\n\n🏷️ Citizens Category Prizing:\n · Free for members\n · $30 for non-members\n\n🏷️ Early 🐣 Registration Open Pricing:\nFeb 23 - March 22\n · $40 for members\n · $70 for non-members\n\n🏷️ Late ⏰ Registration Open Pricing:\nMarch 23 - March 27\n · $60 for members\n · $90 for non-members\n\n🏷️ Spectating:\nOn March 27\n · Free for all\nOn March 28 (after 6pm):\n · Free for members\n · $10 for non-members\n\nJoin us for a whole day of high-level competition, community celebration, and climbing party extravaganza as we highlight the evolution of 🛸 Battle of the Bay 🛸 and the excitement of sport climbing 🥳 at our very first gym.\n\n#missioncliffsclimbing #BattleoftheBay #bayareaclimbing #sportclimbing #touchstoneclimbing",
