    "caption": "⚡️ Woman Up 2026 ⚡️\nFirst ROPED Woman Up competition ever\nCalling📢 all women and non-binary routesetters \n\nAs the largest women’s and non-binary rock-climbing competition on this, or any side of the Sierra, Woman Up is set by women and non-binary setters, for women and non-binary climbers. \n\nHeld at @class5gym in Torrance on Aug 22-23, this year is our first-ever roped-climbing Woman Up, and our routesetter’s application is now officially open 🙌.\n\nThis is an amazing opportunity to both use and up-level your routesetting skillz 😎. Here are the criteria we use during our selection process:\n⚡️Women and non-binary\n⚡️Skill & Experience\n⚡️Mentorship & Growth Potential\n\nSkill & experience usually mean USAC levels and competition experience (as a competitor or routesetter). But this is balanced by our desire to provide avenues for growth and mentorship.\n\nLearn more and apply at the link 🔗 in our bio. \n\n#womanup2025 #womanup #touchstoneclimbing #laclimbing #class5climbing",
